summary: This is an FBI 302 form documenting a proffer interview with Omar Deleon conducted at the U.S. Attorney's Office in Manhattan on August 26, 2019. The document notes the presence of law enforcement agents and Deleon's counsel, and references attached AUSA notes for further information. The main body of the document appears to be heavily redacted or corrupted, with only fragments of text visible.
